### PART VII: APPENDICES (4 pages)

#### A. Glossary of Terms

**Zc (Cognitive Impedance):** Ratio of info generation to processing bandwidth  
**GUSH:** Time-boxed convergence session  
**BHO:** Branching for High-Output (fork operation)  
**BLUES:** Asynchronous rhythm protocol  
**BEACON:** Emergency help signal  
**Micro-GUSH:** 15-30 min mini-GUSH for quick blockers  
**G-Set:** Grow-only set (CRDT operation)  
**MVR:** Multi-value register (preserves divergent views)  
**LWW:** Last-write-wins (idempotent operation)

